<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-69-0137 </DOCNO><TEXT>The present article summarises the project carried out by Coal Mines'Promotion (PMC) and which was partially subsidised by Ocicarbon. Theaim of the project was to improve the process carried out in the SanAntonio colliery washery by recovering the coal contained in collierydiscard. It has proved possible to recover this coal content by treatingthe discard in a fine grinder then feeding it into Reitchert spiral washers.</TEXT></DOC>